description: Point of Care Nano-Technology, Inc. does not have significant operations. Previously, the company was engaged in the development and manufacture of saliva-based medical diagnosis products. It intends to pursue new business opportunities in the life sciences industry. The company was formerly known as Unique Growing Solutions, Inc. and changed its name to Point of Care Nano-Technology, Inc. in March 2015. Point of Care Nano-Technology, Inc. was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Davenport, Florida.
